    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>パレスセダム軍が、
パレスグドラ領を侵犯</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Palace Sedamyu's army has invaded
Palace Gudora's territory.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>国民の８割が
戦禍に巻き込まれ死亡。
都市機能は完全に停止</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Damage to the country has risen by 8% with casualties
constantly on the rise. Small towns have shuttered
operations and have entered a state of emergency. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL check 

used to be 
The damage of the country has risen by 8%. The number
of casualties is constantly on the rise. At this time all
minor towns have ceased their economical functions
completely and entered a state of emergency.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>パレスグドラが降伏するのは
時間の問題です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Palace Gudora's surrender is imminent.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……本当にそうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Is that so?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はっ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah....?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>このまま、パレスグドラが
おとなしく降伏すると思うか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you really believe Palace Gudora
will surrender obediently at this point?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はっ……もはや、
パレスグドラには何の力も
残されておりません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>B-But even if they don't want to...
they currently lack the military
capabilities to make any demands.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何故、パレスグドラが、
何かしらの力を
温存していると考えない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And what if, by chance, they have some sort
of weapon they haven't decided to use yet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270240</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのような力があるなら、
こうなる前に使っていたでしょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I believe if they had such firepower,
they'd have used it already.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうはできない理由が
あるとすれば？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But they could have had a
reason not to use it, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>使うことで、
自らも被害をこうむる、
そんな力ならば？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What if when used, that weapon will
cause collateral damage to them too?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270592</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな力を使えば、
自滅するだけでは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If they possessed such a weapon,
using it would be akin to suicide.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだ、自滅だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, they'd destroy themselves.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>滅びようとする者が
なりふり構わなくなると
講じる手段だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It would mean their situation is so dire
they care not about mutual annihilation.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんとかせねばならぬ、
最悪の事態になる前に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If that is the case, and we
reach a worst case scenario...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_030_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しかし……
今の私に何が、
できる……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet...what could I possibly do...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
